Package hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.exec.functions

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IFunction
    Interface for functions that uses Stack and RequestContext for preforming operations called by method apply.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that adds two numbers.
    DecFmtFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that applys specified format on a number.
    DivFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that divides two numbers.
    DupFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that duplicates value on stack.
    MulFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that multiplies two numbers.
    ParamGetFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that gets parameter from RequestContext defined by name from last element on Stack and pushes fetched element on Stack.
    PparamDelFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that removes parameter, defined by name as peek element on Stack, from persistent parameters in RequestContext
    PparamGetFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that gets parameter, defined by name as peek element on Stack, from persistent parameters in RequestContext and stores it on Stack.
    PparamSetFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that sets parameter, defined by name as peek element on Stack, in persistent parameters in RequestContext with value as second last element on Stack.
    SetMimeTypeFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that sets mime type for RequestContext
    SinFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that pops last value from stack and pushes sinus of that value as result on stack.
    SubFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that subrtacts last two values from stack, pops them and pushes result on stack
    SwapFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that swaps last two elements on stack.
    TparamDelFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that removes parameter, defined by name as peek element on Stack, from temporary parameters in RequestContext
    TparamGetFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that gets parameter, defined by name as peek element on Stack, from temporary parameters in RequestContext and stores it on Stack.
    TparamSetFunction
    Implementation of IFunction that sets parameter, defined by name as peek element on Stack, in temporary parameters in RequestContext with value as second last element on Stack.
